# UI Steps Guide

UI Steps provide custom visualizations in the Motia Workbench.

## Configuration
```typescript
type UiConfig = {
  type: 'ui';
  name: string;
  component: string; // React component name
  props?: Record<string, any>;
}
```

## Component Examples

### Data Display
```typescript
// Custom visualization component
export const DataVisualization = ({ data }) => {
  return (
    <div className="data-viz">
      <h3>{data.title}</h3>
      <pre>{JSON.stringify(data.content, null, 2)}</pre>
    </div>
  );
};

// Step configuration
export const config = {
  type: 'ui',
  name: 'data-display',
  component: 'DataVisualization'
};
```